llm_summary: Gate.io will delist Formation FI (FORM) from trading on September 9, 2024. Withdrawals available for 1 month. Buyback option from September 22, 2024.
Gate.io introduces Smart Arbitrage-USDT to its Quant Fund, offering low entry, high returns, and stability. Min. subscription: 5,000 USDT, 30-day APR: 8.84%.
Mao (MAO) token available for GT subscription on Gate.io from Sep 13-14, 2024. Trading starts Sep 14, 2024. Ensure 10 GT holding to participate.
Gate.io launches SOL Staking, offering flexible asset management with instant redemption and daily rewards. Start staking with just 0.1 SOL.
Gate.io will rebrand DeFi Box (BOX) to DEFIBOX, suspending BOX services from Sep 6, 2024, 06:00 UTC. No blockchain migration; users need no action.
Frontier (FRONT) tokens will migrate to Self Chain (SLF) at a 1:1 ratio. Gate.io will handle the swap. FRONT services will be suspended from August 28, 2024.
